These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, surfing, skateboarding, weightlifting
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, may, december, october
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in december##2
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | weightlifting | swimming     | skateboarding | surfing |
| Birthday     | june     | december | october  | may      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, rock-climbing, camping
City: rome, liverpool, venice, hamburg
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Hobby   | drawing | sudoku    | camping     | rock-climbing  |
| City     | rome    | venice | liverpool | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, juice
4 different games are played: billiard, poker, snooker, whist
1. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | coffee   | cola   | almond-milk  | juice |
| Game           | poker | whist | snooker | billiard  |

