.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, disco, country
City: berlin, boston, new-york, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of country is between the fan of classical and the person traveling to new-york##2
3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | metal | classical | country | disco  |
| City   | boston  | berlin   | venice  | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, siglo, prince, swisher
City: nizza, boston, miami, rome
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
4. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to rome is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | blend    | siglo   | prince | swisher    |
| City      | boston | nizza | miami       | rome |

