.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, amaryllis, orchid
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, house, techno, metal
1. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the fan of techno is between the fan of metal and the person who growsamaryllis##2
3. the fan of salsa is between the fan of techno and the person who growszinnia##2
4. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Flower    | zinnia | amaryllis | orchid | lily |
| Music-Genre   | house | salsa  | techno    | metal  |

