.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks, drawing, filmmaking
There 4 different types of food: avocado, nectarine, cucumber, carrot
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
5. the person eating nectarine is the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person eating nectarine is between the person eating cucumber and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | reading | filmmaking | drawing | magic-tricks     |
| Food     | avocado | carrot  | nectarine   | cucumber |

