.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, corn, zucchini, cranberry
4 different pets are kept: bird, pony, goldfish, frog
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating cranberry is the owner of the pony##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating corn##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food         | cranberry | zucchini | cauliflower | corn   |
| Pet   | pony | goldfish | bird      | frog |

