.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, analyst, lawyer, teacher
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the designer##1
2. the teacher is on the far right##1
3. the teacher is the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the analyst and the designer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage     | tea | iced-tea   | mirinda      | water      |
| Job   | analyst     | lawyer | designer | teacher |

