.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, february, november
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, scrabble, backgammon
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing monopoly##2
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Birthday   | august | april | february      | november   |
| Game   | scrabble  | monopoly    | whist | backgammon |

