.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, monopoly, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, handball, tennis
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Game       | whist | monopoly | scrabble    | mah-jongg      |
| Sport   | handball       | tennis       | snowboarding | sailing |

