.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, lemon, kale, apricot
4 different games are played: poker, domino, monopoly, snooker
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
5. the person eating kale is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Food   | orange     | lemon  | apricot | kale |
| Game     | poker | snooker | domino     | monopoly    |

