.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, r&b, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, taxi, snowmobile
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
2. the fan of funk is the fan of funk##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
4. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
6. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | funk | r&b  | electronic | hip-hop |
| Transport           | taxi     | snowmobile | car    | roller     |

