2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | january  | june | may  | december      |
| Pet    | cat | pony | goldfish | goat |

