.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, montecristo, dunhill, davidoff
City: san-francisco, prague, london, miami
1. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person traveling to prague is the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
6. the person traveling to london is the game-smoker##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | montecristo | davidoff | dunhill | game |
| City   | miami     | san-francisco       | prague   | london      |

