.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg, canasta
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, august, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta | mah-jongg | snooker |
| Birthday         | september  | august   | may | march     |

