.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
City: rome, miami, prague, san-francisco
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, boat, ship
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| City      | rome | miami    | san-francisco  | prague |
| Transport   | helicopter       | snowmobile | boat | ship  |

