.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
House: tower, futuristic, ranch-style, townhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, prince, cain, montecristo
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the futuristic house is the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
4. the townhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the cain-smoker is between the townhouse house and the montecristo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| House   | ranch-style | futuristic  | tower  | townhouse |
| Cigar           | pall-mall    | montecristo | cain | prince |

