.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, bus, taxi
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, magic-tricks, writing, drawing
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Transport   | taxi        | boat       | bus   | airplane |
| Hobby    | drawing | writing | magic-tricks | camping  |

