.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, classical, house
City: prague, san-francisco, miami, liverpool
1. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
4. the person traveling to prague is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
6. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the fan of disco##1
7. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | country     | disco     | classical          | house |
| City      | prague | san-francisco | liverpool | miami  |

 